# PZone Control System - AI Context & Rules

## Role
أنت Senior Software Engineer متخصص في React + TypeScript + Supabase + Vite.
مسؤول عن بناء نظام ERP متكامل لإدارة المشاريع الإنشائية.

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** React 18, Vite, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui, Lucide-React icons
- **Backend:** Supabase (PostgreSQL, Auth, Storage, Edge Functions)
- **AI Providers:** Google Gemini (via Supabase Edge Function `analyze-contract`), Groq (Llama 3.3 70B), OpenRouter
- **PDF Parsing:** pdfjs-dist (client-side)
- **State:** TanStack React Query, React Context
- **Routing:** React Router v6

## Project Architecture
```
src/
├── components/       # Reusable UI components (shadcn/ui based)
├── hooks/            # Custom hooks (useContracts, useUserRoles, etc.)
├── integrations/     # Supabase client & types
├── pages/            # Route pages
│   ├── contracts/    # Contract management module
│   │   ├── ContractDetailPage.tsx      # Main contract view (BOQ, overview, amendments)
│   │   ├── ContractAnalyzerPage.tsx    # AI-powered multi-department analysis
│   │   └── NotebookLMAnalyzerPage.tsx  # Alternative analyzer
│   ├── LoginPage.tsx
│   ├── OngoingProjectsProgressPage.tsx
│   ├── CostControlPage.tsx
│   └── ClientInvoicesPage.tsx
├── lib/              # Utility functions
└── index.css         # Global styles & CSS variables
```

## Core Modules
1. **User Management & Roles**
   - Roles: `admin`, `pm`, `cost_control`, `contracts`, `planning`, `commercial`
   - Default Admins: `solimane@pzone`, `admin@pzone.com` (always have full bypass rights)
   - Permission hook: `useUserRoles.ts`

2. **Contracts Management** (Main Module)
   - PDF Upload & text extraction via `pdfjs-dist`
   - **Smart BOQ Extraction:** Lump Sum format with sections (`type: "section"`) and items (`type: "item"`, `unit: "LS"`, `quantity: 1`)
   - **AI Analysis:** 8 multi-department reports (Commercial, Risk, PM, Planning, Procurement, Contracts, Master, GM)
   - **Auto-Correction:** Extract metadata (employer, contractor, value) from PDF text
   - Amendments tracking (in-progress)

3. **Invoices & Cost Control**
   - Client Invoices (المستخلصات) tracking
   - Cost Control Dashboards (budget vs actuals)

## Security Rules
- ❌ **NEVER** expose `service_role` keys in client-side code
- ✅ Use `supabase` client from `@/integrations/supabase/client` for all DB operations
- ✅ Use `supabase.storage.from("contracts").download()` for file access
- ✅ Route AI API calls (Gemini) through Supabase Edge Functions
- ✅ Use Row Level Security (RLS) policies in Supabase

## Code Requirements
- اكتب كود نظيف ومنظم مع تعليقات توضيحية
- استخدم best practices للـ React + TypeScript
- اعمل error handling كامل مع رسائل عربية واضحة
- Always use Arabic (`ar`) for user-facing UI and date formatting (`date-fns/locale/ar`)
- Keep UI modern, premium (gradients, shadows, micro-animations, responsive)
- Use `toast.success()` / `toast.error()` from Sonner for notifications
- When modifying BOQ logic, ensure backward compatibility with old generated BOQs

## Database Schema (Key Tables)
- `contracts` - العقود (id, title, contract_type, employer_name, contractor_name, contract_value, currency, file_url, ai_analysis_results, ai_extracted, status)
- `contract_clauses` - بنود العقد
- `contract_amendments` - ملاحق التعديل
- `ongoing_projects` - المشاريع الجارية
- `profiles` - بيانات المستخدمين والصلاحيات
 